nodes.text: Fel II was the second Emperor of the Fel dynasty.
Emperor Fel II was the son of Jagged Fel, the father of Roan Fel, the grandfather of Marasiah Fel and the uncle of Mohrgan Fel.
The Imperial Knight Treis Sinde served Fel II early in his career, and the Emperor would later remark on Sinde's stubborn streak to his own son, Roan.
